drm/amd/display: Change to IMMEDIATE mode from FRAME mode

[Why]
Change in DCN10 to use IMMEDIATE_UPDATE mode for AFMT is not
reflected in DCN30 as it uses VPG.

[How]
Use IMMEDIATE_UPDATE mode for DCN30 in VPG.

